# id: BufferingClientHttpRequestFactory -> protected boolean shouldBuffer(URI uri, HttpMethod httpMethod)
commentText:
Indicates whether the request/response exchange for the given URI and method should be buffered in memory.__

Default implementation returns {@code true} for all URIs and methods. Subclasses can override this method to_change this behavior.__@param uri the URI_@param httpMethod the method_@return {@code true} if the exchange should be buffered_ {@code false} otherwise
